headline: Palantir initiated, Roku upgraded: Wall Street’s top analyst calls
summary: The most talked about and market moving research calls around Wall Street are now in one place. Here are today’s research calls that investors need to know, as compiled by The Fly. Top 5 Upgrades: Jefferies upgraded Roku (ROKU) to Hold from Underperform with a price target of $100, up from $55, following the Q4 outperformance. Roku’s 25% year-over-year Platform growth was well ahead of its guidance as the company executes on third party integrations and improving fill rates, the firm tells inves
